title: Happy Hour #75: SMNTY Makes a Summer Cocktail, Part 2

description:
Anney divulges the recipe for her cocktail 'That's So Feetch' (spoiler alert, it's basically a paloma), and Samantha tries to get to the bottom of why Anney likes puns and naming things.
